       EEEExxxxppppeeeerrrrtttt AAAAccccttttiiiivvvvaaaattttiiiioooonnnn
                 Some elements, usually PushButtons and ToggleBut-
                 tons, can have expert actions associated with
                 them.  BBBBSSSSeeeelllleeeecccctttt CCCClllliiiicccckkkk 2222 must activate any expert
                 action for the element.  Expert action should only
                 be available in a Panel, and the expert action of
                 all the buttons should be similar.  The expert
                 action should include the regular action of the
                 component in a more global manner.

